storyInfo: Popukar and Bubble find themselves bored after an episode of their favorite cartoon and start thinking of games to play. Just then, Bubble catches a glimpse of the 'secret' that lies under Popukar's eyepatch, and soâ€”

attributes.content: Rhodes Island Landship, Common Rest Area Passageway
The end.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: That's it?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: When's the next episode?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I'll ask.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Shamare, when can we watch 'Felitubbies' episode 20?
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Zzzz...
attributes.name: Shamare

attributes.content: Looks like she fell asleep while we were watching.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: She's been doing that a lot.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Isn't 'Felitubbies' fun though?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Spot says it's for kids.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Maybe Shamare got too big for it?
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: No way!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: She's only a few years older than us! Just two episodes ago, she was with us for the whole thing! How could she fall asleep on us this time?!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: We'll grow up really, really soon too. Maybe we'll be grown-ups by the time we finish the show.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: What do you want to do when you grow up, Bubble?
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Me? I'm gonna go back to my tribe and beat up everyone I don't like and become a great warrior!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: What 'bout you?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I wanna be a superhero. I'll knock out bad guys with one punch, shoot eye lasers, and fly through the sky.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Do superheroes really exist?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I've never seen anyone shoot beams out their eyes or anyone who knows how to fly.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I know lots who beat up bad guys, though.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Like me.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: That's just what I want to become...
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: My eye has been sick for so long, I've been thinking how cool it would be if I could shoot lasers out of my eyes like a superhero.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: I hope you get better! I want to see both your eyes!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: When my bad eye gets better, you'll be the first one to see it.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Really?! Hooray!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Hehe.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Hmm...
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: What time is it?
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Hm...
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Orchid told us we could play for two hours. We only have half an hour left.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Why only two hours? Can't we play all hours?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: We have training and school. We need to do our homework, too. The teacher will be mad if we don't.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Why do we have to do homework?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: We need to study hard. That's what the adults always tell us.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: I've been running all around the ship every day. I've never heard anything about homework.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: And um, what is homework actually? Is it tasty?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I don't think you can eat it. Homework'sâ€”Hm... I'm not sure what exactly homework is either. I just know you get smarter if you do it.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Why don't you give it a try?
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Is this homework?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Yes.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: It's just a book.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Did you draw all these things?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Most of them.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: But the red ink ones are the teacher.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: I don't get it at all.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Ugh, you can have it back.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: If they make me learn this stuff, I'm gonna jump off the ship and run straight home to Papa in Sargon.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: And if anyone stands in my way, I'll trample them!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I heard what happened with that lady from Minos a few days agoâ€”
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Nothing happened! You heard wrong!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: That Forte's not so strong!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I smashed her into the ground easy!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Uh-huh.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Really! I did!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: If you swear on your Papa, I'll believe you.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Ugh...
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Fine! I will!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I, Bubble, swear by Papa's name... that I couldn't beat the Minoan Forte lady.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: So you lied. It did happen.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Don't tell anyone! I'm really not so weak, really really!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: The Forte lady is just way too strong!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Okay, I see. You tell the truth every time you swear.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: W-What can I do? Papa said that if you swear something by someone's name, that person'll hear it!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: If Papa finds out I lied, he'll whoop my butt so hard!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: So if I swear something by my dad's name, will he hear what I say too?
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: I dunno. Why don't you try?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: My dad. His nameâ€”
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Hmm...
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: I don't remember his name.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: What about your mama? That works too.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I don't remember hers either.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Auntie Kal'tsit said I was sculpted out of clay.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: But I think I had parents too.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Everyone else has parents. There's no way I don't.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: You're right.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Maybe the white coat doctor was lying to you?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I don't think Auntie Kal'tsit lies.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: The Feline doctor, right? I can tell from the look on her face, she's a bad woman. Not like my shaman grandpa back home. He's always smiling. One look at him and you know he's nice.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Being quiet doesn't make someone a baddie.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Look at Shamare.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Shamare always looks really cold too, but she takes care of everyone.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: That one time you ate a cactus and got needles all stuck in your mouth, she was the one who knocked you out cold and plucked out every last one before she turned you over to the doctors.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Oh...
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: And she knows how to pick good apples. Her apples are so big, sweet, and tasty.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: You're right. She does bring us really tasty apples.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Okay, I believe you. Shamare's not a baddie, and that doctor isn't a baddie either.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: But if no one's bad, and the doctor didn't lie to you, then how come you don't remember your mama or your papa?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Maybe it's because I have a bad memory. I forget lots of things.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: But there are things I won't forget.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: The banging sounds in the mines, the big steel cities, way bigger than Rhodes Island, and the towers surrounded by tons of people.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: There was a doctor wearing a big white coat, a bunch of glittering chunks of steel, and a small, quiet room.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: There was also a big white room with a bed inside.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Sounds like you remember a lot, actually.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: But I don't remember my mom and dad's names...
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Hm...
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Maybe you'll remember when you get your head knocked around. That's how I usually remember things.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I can give you a good whack, if you want!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I'm really strong!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Whap whap whap!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: You're too strong, Bubble. You'll smack me so hard I'll turn dumb.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Really? I guess I won't do that then.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Buzz, buzz.
Hmm...
attributes.name: Shamare

attributes.content: This is boring. Look, Shamare's even talking in her sleep. Popukar, lemme play with your brum brum brrrrr thing a little.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Okay, but the brum brum brrrr thing won't go brrrr today.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Why?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: The thing that makes it go brrrr is being fixed.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: It broke when I was helping everyone else brrrr things.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Oh.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I'll think of something else to play, then.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: You should spend less time on training and classes and play more like me, Popukar. That other stuff is boring.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: But if we don't keep up with our training, we might get hurt when we go beat up the baddies.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Besides, I need to help out Orchid, and everyone else.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: You're such a goody two-shoes! You should be like me. Grab a shield and charge straight ahead.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: That's a good way to get hurt.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: When I started out, I didn't know what I was doing. I took my brum brum brrrr thing and swung it all over the place, and it got people hurt sometimes, people I didn't wanna hurt.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Then I started training and I learned to listen to Orchid. She does the thinking, and I do the listening.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: That way I won't get hurt, and neither does anybody else. I think it's a nice thing.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: The people you don't wanna hurt, are they strong? Like, as strong as Papa?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I don't think so, but they take good care of me.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Orchid combs my hair, and Midnight picks out clothes for me.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Catapult brings me tasty food, and Spot finds me fun comics to read.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Wowâ€”That does sound nice! I should get the Doctor to find me some servants too.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: But how come you still chase them with your brum brum brrrr thing?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Brum brum brrrr thing? Chase who?
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: I wouldn't do that.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Shamare always says she's a big girl and so nobody's allowed to pat her head.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: But she actually gets all happy whenever she gets a headpat.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Shamare does?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Yep!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Oh, I have an idea! Shamare's tail is so much fun to play with. Wanna try?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: It's so smooth and soft. Not even the beast hide on Papa's throne is that smooth.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Shamare will get mad.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: She's asleep! She doesn't have to know!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: But what if she wakes up?
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Hrmph.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Let me think of something else...
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: We could wrestle?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Orchid says we're not allowed to wrestle in the lounge. She says it could disturb someone's rest.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: You listen to everything she says? Sheesh...
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I'll keep an eye... on her...
attributes.name: Shamare

attributes.content: Poor Shamare. So bored she's talking in her sleep.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: There's gotta be something fun we can do...?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I got it!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Let's arm wrestle! That's safe enough, right?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: It's quiet, we get to see which one of us's stronger, and most importantlyâ€”
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: We've never done it before.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I guess.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Let's use this table, then. Come!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Ready?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Yeah.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Hmph!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Ahh!
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: I've never lost an arm wrestling match...
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Hnggh! Haah!
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: By Papa's name!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I will never lose at arm wrestling!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Haah!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Hyah!
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: W-We broke the table...
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: (Whispers) W-What do we do?
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: (Whispers) I dunno!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Zzzz...
attributes.name: Shamare

attributes.content: That was close. But she's still asleep.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: If we woke her up, she'd curse me for sure.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: W-What about the table?
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Let the janitor take care of it!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: But what if the janitor asks? W-What do we tell him?
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: We'll tell him it broke on its own!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: It's not good to lie...
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: I don't want a spanking!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Spankings are worse than lying!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: *Whimpers*...
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Okay, when the adults show up, we'll tell them the table broke on its own. Okay?!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Okay...
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Hm, your eyepatch's tilted.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: There's something black inside...
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: (Readjusts eyepatch hurriedly)
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Is that black thing those bad rocks?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Maybe. I didn't touch it.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Orchid and Auntie Kal'tsit told me to never take my eyepatch off.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Why?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I don't remember...
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Then let me take a look, okay? Just a peek. You can put it right back. It'll be fine.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Hm...
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: I'll share my snacks with you. I got a really tasty box from the fat purple Vulpo girl last week.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: And it's your favorite wafers!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Deal?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Okay...
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Just a peek, though.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Okay!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Hehe!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Mmm...
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: What's wrong?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: I-It's too bright...
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Hold on! I'll turn off the lights!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: (Opens eyes)...
attributes.name: Shamare

attributes.content: Is it okay now?
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Hmm...
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: (Takes off eyepatch)
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Whoa, that's so cool!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Really?
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: It looks so nice, so cool!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: What is it like?
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: I dunno, but it's super cool.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Hm? Something looks kinda shiny inside.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Ohâ€”
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Whoa, it's getting shinier!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Your eye's so awesome!
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: It's kinda hot too.
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: What's going on?
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Put your eyepatch on.
attributes.name: Shamare

attributes.content: Okay, Shamare.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Hey, Shamare, what are youâ€”
attributes.name: Bubble

attributes.content: Eh?
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Orchid's outside the door. Don't keep her waiting.
attributes.name: Shamare

attributes.content: Orchid? Already? I gotta go!
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: But what about Bubble?
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: I'll take her back to the dorm.
attributes.name: Shamare

attributes.content: Okay.
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: Then I'll get going. See you!
attributes.name: Popukar

attributes.content: See ya.
attributes.name: Shamare

attributes.content: Phew...
attributes.name: Shamare

attributes.content: Buzz, buzz.
Yes.
attributes.name: Shamare

attributes.content: Popukar is fine.
attributes.name: Shamare

attributes.content: Yes.
attributes.name: Shamare

attributes.content: I'll bring Bubble right now.
attributes.name: Shamare

attributes.content: Let's go, Morte. We're dragging Bubble to Medical.
attributes.name: Shamare

attributes.content: I hope she learned her lesson this time.
attributes.name: Shamare

attributes.content: Yes, drag. She's too heavy. We can't carry her.
attributes.name: Shamare

attributes.content: Let's go.
attributes.name: Shamare
